---
title: Quick & Cheesy Scrambled Egg Migas Tacos with Pico de Gallo & Tortilla Chips
description: Take your morning to new heights with quick, easy, cheesy scrambled egg tacos, on the table in just 20 minutes. You’ll sprinkle warm flour tortillas with our melty Mexican cheese blend, then fill with Mexican-spiced scallion scrambled eggs. Top those off with crushed blue corn tortilla chips for crunch (that’s where the migas come in—Spanish for “crumbs”), plus pico de gallo, sour cream, and a drizzle of hot sauce, and watch your morning go from ho-hum to absolutely delectable!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cca7cbcc89468059ab0014-236b7b8e.jpeg
